object.name: text
object.text: Guess I'll be needing a new hunting party... But that bounty on your head will buy a whole army.

object.name: text
object.text: Why does some stupid money make you want to hurt us? I don't understand it!

object.name: text
object.text: We could have been your friends. We had so much to share with you!

object.name: text
object.text:
Charity from a monster!
God forbid a man sink so low!

object.name: text
object.text: It's His will that we fight for what's ours! The only nice thing I need is your corpse for that bounty!
